attributionInfo.brokerName: Berkshire Hathaway Home Services California Properties

data.description: Enjoy the resort lifestyle, Leave the big city behind buy in the Desert where your money buy you more house for the Dollar. Recently renovated, this two story, app 2900 ft. light an open floor plan with lots of windows. 6 bedrooms and 3 baths, one bedroom located downstairs large Central kitchen upgraded to handle demands of the living room, game room and formal dining. Property has upgraded air conditioning and solar panels that are bought and paid for keep it as cool as you want in the house. Open up the sliding doors and get ready to enjoy the your own resort backyard complete with a custom pool and spa, lots of area to have a barbecue, parties, entertain or just enjoying the spectacular mountain views. This home is perfect for a family vacation resort property or a really nice primary home.
